OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FEarly
OL,6,Fevening sunny spells will gradually
OL,7,Fgive way to thickening cloud and
OL,8,Foutbreaks of rain spreading east,
OL,9,Fthese occasionally heavy. Largely dry
OL,10,Fby dawn, with just isolated showers.
OL,11,FTurning a little breezy, but mild.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FA mostly cloudy start with
OL,14,Fisolated showers, mainly over the
OL,15,FPennines. Sunny spells developing with
OL,16,Fshowers dying out completely for the
OL,17,Fafternoon. Breezy, and cooler than of
OL,18,Flate.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
