OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FTurning more unsettled. Stronger
OL,7,Fwinds, rain and showers, with possible
OL,8,Fhail and thunder on Tuesday,
OL,9,Finterspersed with drier and brighter
OL,10,Finterludes. Temperatures near normal,
OL,11,Ffeeling fresher than recently.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
